  "detailed_description": "Make It Count is a <strong>1-3 players Co-op, post-apocalyptic, top-down shooter with roguelite elements</strong>.<br>As the last survivors of humanity, it is your duty to exterminate this filth from the infested earth. Set out on your mission and get stronger by finding various <strong>trinkets!</strong> Collect meaningful resources to unlock, upgrade weapons and classes. Quench your bloodlust by eradicating these abominations!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>MAKE IT COUNT</li></ul></strong>Ammo is limited in Make It Count, it is not scarce but you have to make your shots count! Scavenging ammo and other useful things on missions is a must! Or you can always pull out your melee weapon and slash!<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>MISSION</li></ul></strong>Different paths may open up for each run! Routes will be randomized, it is not infinite but will provide variety for different mini-missions in-game and trinkets!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/596a57ca6c56c0cabda332de43e664bf.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/596a57ca6c56c0cabda332de43e664bf.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>FOG OF WAR</li></ul></strong>Be careful! Your vision is limited and danger lurks everywhere!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/dee718849f4f051f8f57ec78b0bb500c.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/dee718849f4f051f8f57ec78b0bb500c.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>CUSTOMIZATION</li></ul></strong>When chilling out in your HUB area, you can upgrade your weapons and characters. That’s not all! You can also craft various decorations in your HUB to make it visually appealing to your eye!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/312ade6b8eca6434e63b488e0c605212.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/312ade6b8eca6434e63b488e0c605212.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Make It Count is a <strong>1-3 players Co-op, post-apocalyptic, top-down shooter with roguelite elements</strong>.<br>As the last survivors of humanity, it is your duty to exterminate this filth from the infested earth. Set out on your mission and get stronger by finding various <strong>trinkets!</strong> Collect meaningful resources to unlock, upgrade weapons and classes. Quench your bloodlust by eradicating these abominations!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>MAKE IT COUNT</li></ul></strong>Ammo is limited in Make It Count, it is not scarce but you have to make your shots count! Scavenging ammo and other useful things on missions is a must! Or you can always pull out your melee weapon and slash!<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>MISSION</li></ul></strong>Different paths may open up for each run! Routes will be randomized, it is not infinite but will provide variety for different mini-missions in-game and trinkets!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/596a57ca6c56c0cabda332de43e664bf.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/596a57ca6c56c0cabda332de43e664bf.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>FOG OF WAR</li></ul></strong>Be careful! Your vision is limited and danger lurks everywhere!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/dee718849f4f051f8f57ec78b0bb500c.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/dee718849f4f051f8f57ec78b0bb500c.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>CUSTOMIZATION</li></ul></strong>When chilling out in your HUB area, you can upgrade your weapons and characters. That’s not all! You can also craft various decorations in your HUB to make it visually appealing to your eye!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/312ade6b8eca6434e63b488e0c605212.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/312ade6b8eca6434e63b488e0c605212.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
